<body>

  <h1>Python Set Operators Cheat Sheet</h1>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Operator</th>
        <th>Symbol</th>
        <th>Heuristic / Mnemonic</th>
        <th>Plain English</th>
        <th>Example Result<br>(A={1,2,3,4}, B={3,4,5,6})</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Union</td>
        <td>|</td>
        <td class="mnemonic">me <strong>plus</strong> you</td>
        <td>Everyone in at least one set</td>
        <td>{1,2,3,4,5,6}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Intersection</td>
        <td>&</td>
        <td class="mnemonic">both me <strong>and</strong> you</td>
        <td>Only items in both sets</td>
        <td>{3,4}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Difference</td>
        <td>-</td>
        <td class="mnemonic">in me <strong>but not</strong> in you</td>
        <td>Items only in left set</td>
        <td>{1,2}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Symmetric Difference</td>
        <td>^</td>
        <td class="mnemonic">in me <strong>XOR</strong> in you<br>(exclusive friends)</td>
        <td>Items in exactly one set</td>
        <td>{1,2,5,6}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Subset</td>
        <td>&lt;=</td>
        <td class="mnemonic">I'm completely <strong>inside</strong> you</td>
        <td>Left ≤ Right</td>
        <td>False</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Proper subset</td>
        <td>&lt;</td>
        <td class="mnemonic">I'm <strong>strictly inside</strong> you</td>
        <td>Left < Right</td>
        <td>False</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Superset</td>
        <td>&gt;=</td>
        <td class="mnemonic">I <strong>contain</strong> you completely</td>
        <td>Left ≥ Right</td>
        <td>False</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Proper superset</td>
        <td>&gt;</td>
        <td class="mnemonic">I <strong>strictly contain</strong> you</td>
        <td>Left > Right</td>
        <td>False</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="quick">
    Quick reminders:  
    <strong>A | B</strong> → me plus you  •  
    <strong>A & B</strong> → both  •  
    <strong>A - B</strong> → me but not you  •  
    <strong>A ^ B</strong> → exclusive / surprise guests
  </div>

